#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/Eastern_Flank.cfg:4
msgid "The Eastern Flank"
msgstr "Il fianco orientale"

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/Eastern_Flank.cfg:9
msgid ""
"After breaking out of their encirclement, the party continued in pursuit of "
"the trolls."
msgstr ""
"Dopo aver rotto l'accerchiamento, il gruppo continuò l'inseguimento dei "
"troll."

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/Eastern_Flank.cfg:14
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"They soon lost all hope of recovering their gold, hoping only to reach "
"Rakshas before he could use it to raise more troops."
msgstr ""
"Per quanto ormai avessero perso ogni speranza di recuperare l'oro, "
"continuarono a seguirli, sperando di raggiungere Rakshas prima che riuscisse "
"a farne buon uso."

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/Eastern_Flank.cfg:19
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Following the bank of a river, they soon entered a valley. At the mouth of "
"the valley there loomed the massive orcish fortress of Angthurim."
msgstr ""
"Proseguendo lungo la riva di un fiume entrarono in una valle, "
"all'imboccatura della quale c'era una massiccia fortezza degli orchi."

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/Eastern_Flank.cfg:277
msgid ""
"Gods of Light! Look at that fortress.  The castle Angthurim is even grimmer "
"than its reputation."
msgstr ""

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/Eastern_Flank.cfg:290
msgid ""
"I was not idle in my captivity; I watched, and listened, and learned. The "
"hints I got from my guards' boastings and foul jests have been confirmed by "
"our scouts; Angthurim is the linchpin of their entire eastern flank. If we "
"could reduce it, their defense would be near to collapse."
msgstr ""

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/Eastern_Flank.cfg:300
msgid ""
"Fitting. My gryphons tell me Angthurim is the keystone of their entire "
"eastern flank. If we can reduce it their defense will be near to collapse."
msgstr ""

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/Eastern_Flank.cfg:310
#, fuzzy
msgid "Hey, look who is here!"
