msgstr ""

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/Showdown.cfg:736
#, fuzzy
msgid "What the...? How did *he* get here?"
msgstr "Che cosa...? Com'è arrivato là?"

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/Showdown.cfg:749
msgid ""
"We have crushed and scattered your entire eastern flank, and now it's your "
