#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/Showdown.cfg:1023
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"At last! Rakshas has been slain, and the orcish host has been crushed. Peace "
"and prosperity will come to the Northlands once again!"
msgstr ""
"Finalmente! Rakshas è stato ucciso e l'orda degli orchi è stata annientata. "
"La pace e la prosperità torneranno di nuovo alle Terre del Nord."

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/Showdown.cfg:1028
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"At these words all the allied forces gave out a combined and thunderous "
"cheer. Their long ordeal was finally over."
msgstr ""
"A queste parole ogni uomo, elfo, nano, drago, lich, ogre, troll amichevole e "
"grifone rumoreggiò di felicità. Il lungo periodo di difficoltà era alla fine."

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/Showdown.cfg:1034
msgid " *small voice lost in the uproar* Awww, is it over already?"
msgstr ""

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/Showdown.cfg:1051
msgid ""
"Die, you murderous beast! No longer shall you terrorize the people of the "
"North."
msgstr ""

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/Showdown.cfg:1057
#, fuzzy
msgid "Learn the fate of one who offends the Dwarves of Knalga."
msgstr "Guardate il fato di coloro che offendono gli Elfi del Nord."

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/Showdown.cfg:1063
#, fuzzy
msgid "Or the elves of the Northern Forests."
msgstr "O la gente di Porte dei Nani."

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/Showdown.cfg:1074
#, fuzzy
msgid "Or the humans of Dwarven Doors."
msgstr "O la gente di Porte dei Nani."

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/Showdown.cfg:1080
msgid ""
" *gurggle* No!... this.... cannot.... be... happening.... to.... me....."
msgstr ""

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/Showdown.cfg:1086
msgid "Such were the last words of of Rakshas the great!"
msgstr "Ecco le ultime parole di Rakshas il grande!"

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/Showdown.cfg:1107
msgid "Argh!"
msgstr "Argh!"

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/Showdown.cfg:1113
msgid ""
"Hamel! Blast it, without the dwarves to hold the western flank we are as "
