#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:787
msgid ""
"Oh yeah, those things. Watch out, they are the arms of some sort of "
"underwater creature. They'll try to pummel you to death, then drag you under "
"for dinner."
msgstr ""

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:793
msgid ""
"Then how do we get past? I can see that the passage continues to both the "
"north and south and we haven't found Malifor yet..."
msgstr ""

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:799
msgid ""
"Creatures of that type regenerate over time; it's doubtful we can destroy it "
"completely. But if we destroy its arms we'll be relatively safe until they "
"regenerate."
msgstr ""

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:805
msgid "Let's get to it, then."
msgstr ""

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:821
msgid "Hmm, what is this thing?"
msgstr ""

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:838
msgid "EEEEEEEEEEEEEEEE!"
msgstr "EEEEEEEEEEEEEEEE!"

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:843
msgid "AHHHHHHHHH!"
msgstr "AHHHHHHHHH!"

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:849
msgid "... wait a second, who are you?"
msgstr "... aspetta un momento, chi sei?"

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:854
msgid "I.... I am one of Tallin's men..."
msgstr "Io... io sono uni degli uomini di Tallin..."

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:859
msgid "Who is this Tallin?"
msgstr "Chi è questo Tallin?"

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:865
msgid "I am."
msgstr "Sono io."

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:870
msgid "What is your purpose in coming here?"
msgstr "Cosa sei venuto a fare qua?"

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:875
msgid "We seek the lich Malifor."
msgstr "Stiamo cercando il lich Malifor"

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:881
msgid ""
"Malifor!... *goes a bit paler (if possible)* What business do you have with "
"him?"
msgstr ""
"Malifor!... (diventa ancora più pallido - se possibile) Cosa volete da lui?"

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:887
msgid "We seek to crush and destroy him."
msgstr "Lo vogliamo distruggere."

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:893
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Oh, thank the Gods of Light! Finally there is someone here in force to deal "
"with that menace. You must have been sent by the High Kalian of "
"Hiera'Shirsha?"
msgstr ""
"Oh, sia grazie agli dei! Finalmente c'è qualcuno qua con la forza per "
"stroncare questa minaccia. Deve esere stato il supremo Kalian di "
"Hiera'Shirsha a mandarvi?"

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:899
msgid "The what!?"
msgstr "Il supremo cosa?"

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:905
msgid "Err, I think we might be in different... uh... time zones, here."
msgstr "Err, penso che qui siamo in una diversa... eh... «zona temporale»."

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:910
msgid "I beg my pardon. Say, what year is it anyway?"
msgstr "Domando scusa. Dimmi, in che anno siamo?"

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:916
msgid "Uh... 534 YW..."
msgstr ""

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:921
msgid "Huh!? Can't be, the last year I remember it was 14318 AD!"
msgstr ""

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:927
msgid "?????"
msgstr "?????"

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:933
msgid "Different calendars, folks."
msgstr ""

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:939
msgid "I see, but say, who are you?"
msgstr "Lo vedo, ma dimmi: chi sei?"

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:944
msgid "What? How can you not know who I am?"
msgstr "Cosa? Come puoi non sapere chi sono io?"

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:950
msgid "The times have changed, my friend."
msgstr "I tempi cambiano, amico mio."

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:955
msgid ""
"Right... sorry about that. My name is Lord Alfred and I am... or was... the "
"ruler of the great kingdom of Garet-Desh."
msgstr ""
"Bene... sono spiacente. Io sono Lord Alfred e sono... o meglio sono stato... "
"il sovrano del grande regno di Garet-Desh."

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:962
msgid "What happened to you? Why are you a ghost?"
msgstr "Cosa ti è successo? Perché sei diventato un fantasma?"

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:967
msgid ""
"I grew old and died as all men do and entered the land of the dead. I don't "
"know how long I dwelled there, I was wrenched from my peace and forced into "
"this ectoplasmic body by a terrible power."
msgstr ""

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:973
msgid "Let me guess. Malifor?"
msgstr "Lasciami indovinare, Malifor?"

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:978
msgid ""
"Indeed. He tried to break my spirit into mindless slavery, but I resisted "
"his power and fled. I have been hiding in these flooded tunnels ever since. "
"Some monster that Malifor's minions greatly fear lives in these waters; they "
"do not milest me here."
msgstr ""

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:984
msgid "Would you join us to defeat this evil creature?"
msgstr ""

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:989
msgid ""
"Wouldn't miss it. Maybe after he is destroyed me and my kind can live... "
"err.... be dead peacefully."
msgstr ""

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:994
msgid ""
"Keep following these flooded tunnels. I think they might lead you directly "
"to Mailfor."
msgstr ""

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:1000
msgid "Great! Forward, men!"
msgstr ""

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:1013
msgid ""
"Just great, I am cold, wet, and tired and what have we here? Another dead "
"end. This place is starting to get on my nerves!"
msgstr ""

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:1026
msgid "Ssssh! I hear something."
msgstr "Ssssh! Sento qualcosa."

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:1029
msgid "Sea Serpent"
msgstr "Serpente marino"

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:1033
msgid "ROOOAAARRR!"
msgstr "ROOOAAARRR!"

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:1038
msgid "Ahhhhh!"
msgstr "Ahhhhh!"

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:1054
msgid "Hold it, people, there is something just ahead!"
msgstr "Fermi tutti, c'è qualcosa davanti a noi!"

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:1095
msgid " *sniff* I smell humans."
msgstr ""

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:1100
msgid "You are just plain deaf. I heard them coming from a mile off."
msgstr "Sei proprio completamente sordo. Li ho sentiti arrivare da un miglio."

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:1105
msgid "Ahh, shut up. Let's go kill them."
msgstr "Ah, sta' zitto. Facciamoli fuori."

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:1119
msgid "A door, and a big, *big* lock,  Hmmmmm..."
msgstr ""

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:1124
msgid "Sorry folks, this is just too tempting."
msgstr ""

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:1129
#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:1155
msgid " *SMASH*."
msgstr "THUD! CRASH!"

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:1150
msgid ""
"Hmmmm, this door sure is locked up pretty tight. I wonder what's behind it."
msgstr ""

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:1176
msgid ""
"Holy water! For a certainty, those skeletons won't like us getting our hands "
"on this stuff. But that's probably why they kept them back here in the first "
"place."
msgstr ""

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:1190
msgid "Oh yeah, holy water!"
msgstr "Oh sì, acqua benedetta!"

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:1204
#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:1223
msgid ""
"Warning! These bottles contain toxic waste. Causes disintegration on contact."
msgstr ""
"Attenzione! Queste bottiglie contengono rifiuti tossici. Provocano "
"disintegrazione al contatto."

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:1209
msgid "Ha ha, for skeletons anyway."
msgstr "Ah ah, per gli scheletri al meno."

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:1228
msgid " *rolls eyes* Oh the hazardous life of a skeleton."
msgstr "(rotea gli occhi) Oh, la pericolosa vita dello scheletro."

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:1242
msgid "The Treasury"
msgstr "Il tesoro"

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:1247
msgid "The Treasury! Cool, let's go loot some booty!"
msgstr ""

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:1261
msgid "The Dungeon"
msgstr "Le segrete"

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:1276
msgid "Malifor the Great's Study."
msgstr "Il laboratorio del grande Malifor"

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:1281
msgid "There we go! This way guys!"
msgstr "Andiamo di qua! Da questa parte, ragazzi!"

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:1295
msgid "Wow! There is at least 1000 gold in here!"
msgstr "Wow! Ci sono almeno 1000 pezzi d'oro qua!"

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:1316
#, fuzzy
msgid "Holy Gods of Light! 500 gold!"
msgstr "Merda secca! 500 pezzi!"

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:1337
msgid "800 gold! We're rich!!!"
msgstr "800 pezzi! Siamo ricchi!!!"

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:1358
msgid "What a horde! 2 000 gold!"
msgstr "Che tesoro! 2000 pezzi d'oro!"

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:1379
msgid "500 gold! Not bad!"
msgstr "500 pezzi d'oro! Non male!"

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:1400
msgid "1000 gold! Wow! Where is that bag of bones getting all this?"
msgstr "1000 pezzi d'oro! Wow! Dove li ha presi quel sacco d'ossa?"

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:1436
msgid "Freedom at last. Thank you Lord Tallin."
msgstr "Finalmente liberi. Grazie a voi, lord tallin."

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:1443
msgid ""
"Just Tallin. I am no lord, just a humble peasant trying to restore our "
"people to freedom."
msgstr ""
"Chiamami Tallin, non sono un lord, solo un semplice contadino che cerca di "
"restituire la libertà al nostro popolo."

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:1458
#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:1597
msgid "Who are you? How did you end up down here?"
msgstr "Chi sei? Come hai fatto a finire quaggiù?"

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:1462
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"I am called Sister Theta. My husband Marcus and I were advisers and healers "
"for the dwarvish nobles of Knalga. We could not save them from Khazg Black-"
"Tusk's troops, but we survived the orcs and trolls only to be captured when "
"these skeletons appeared."
msgstr ""
"Mi chiamano sorella Theta. Mio marito Marcus e io eravamo i consiglieri e "
"guaritori dei nobili dei nani. Quindi, naturalmente, gli orchi hanno "
"attaccato, seguiti dai troll e poi da questi demoni! Siamo riusciti a "
"sopravvivere in qualche maniera agli orchi e ai troll ma quando sono apparsi "
"questi scheletri ci hanno catturato."

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:1469
msgid ""
"Funny, why would the bonebag keep you as his prisoners? He didn't seem to be "
"the merciful type."
msgstr ""
"Divertente, e perché il «sacco d'ossa» vi avrebbe fatti prigionieri? Non mi "
"pare che sia un tipo misericordioso."

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:1474
#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:1613
msgid ""
"He didn't keep us alive out of mercy, he wanted to study us to see if there "
"was a way to counteract our holy attacks. His kind are very vulnerable to "
"such attacks, as I am sure you know by now."
msgstr ""
"Non ci ha lasciati vivere per pietà, voleva studiarci per vedere se c'era "
"una maniera di rispondere ai nostri attacchi sacri. La sua genia è molto "
"vulnerabile a questi attacchi cosiì come ora certamente lo sapete anche voi."

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:1481
msgid ""
"Yes indeed. But you are now free to go wherever you like. May the Lords of "
"Light guide your path."
msgstr ""
"Sì, effettivamente. Ma comunque sia, ora siete liberi di andare dove volete. "
"Possano i signori della luce guidare la vostra strada.."

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:1486
msgid ""
"If you have no objection, Tallin, we would like to join you. These "
"northlands are hardly safe these days for anyone to be traveling on their "
"own, and we could lend valuable help to your cause."
msgstr ""

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:1493
msgid "Very well, you are most welcome to join us."
msgstr "Benissimo, siete i benvenuti tra di noi."

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:1498
#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:1637
msgid "Thank you, Tallin."
msgstr "Grazie, Tallin."

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:1512
#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:1651
msgid "Marcus!"
msgstr "Marcus!"

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:1518
#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:1657
msgid "Theta!"
msgstr "Theta!"

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:1524
msgid "Please folks, not now."
msgstr "Per favore gente, non adesso."

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:1529
#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:1668
msgid "Oh, sorry."
msgstr "Oh, spiacente."

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:1575
msgid ""
"Finally! I am free. Lord Tallin, I am forever in your debt! We will follow "
"you to the end of the World if need be."
msgstr ""

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:1582
msgid "It's just Tallin, no lord. And no problem."
msgstr "Solo Tallin, niente lord. E non c'è di che."

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:1601
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"I am called Father Marcus. My wife, Theta and I were advisers and healers "
"for the dwarvish nobles. We could not shield them from the wrath of Khazg "
"Black-Tusk, but we survived the orcs and trols -- only to be captured by "
"these skeletons."
msgstr ""
"Mi chiamano sorella Theta. Mio marito Marcus e io eravamo i consiglieri e "
"guaritori dei nobili dei nani. Quindi, naturalmente, gli orchi hanno "
"attaccato, seguiti dai troll e poi da questi demoni! Siamo riusciti a "
"sopravvivere in qualche maniera agli orchi e ai troll ma quando sono apparsi "
"questi scheletri ci hanno catturato."

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:1608
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Funny, why would the bonebag keep you as his prisoners? He doesn't really "
"seem to be the merciful type."
msgstr ""
"Divertente, e perché il «sacco d'ossa» vi avrebbe fatti prigionieri? Non mi "
"pare che sia un tipo misericordioso."

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:1620
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Yes, indeed. But you are now free to go wherever you like. May the Lords of "
"Light guide your path."
msgstr ""
"Sì, effettivamente. Ma comunque sia, ora siete liberi di andare dove volete. "
"Possa il signore della luce guidare la vostra strada.."

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:1625
msgid ""
"As I have said, Tallin, I am eternally in your debt, and I take my debts "
"seriously. If you have no objection, I will serve you until one of us "
"departs this life."
msgstr ""

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:1632
msgid ""
"Oh, think nothing of it. Let no talk of debts come between us; rather let us "
"join hands as allies in restoring these Northlands to sanity."
msgstr ""

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:1663
msgid "Please, folks, not now."
msgstr "Per favore, gente, non adesso."

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:1701
msgid ""
"Wow! That's incredible. Now I understand why the Bag of Bones kept you guys "
"in jail; He just simply couldn't kill you!"
msgstr ""

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:1736
msgid "Oh my, she is almost dead!"
msgstr ""

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:1750
msgid "Here, let me see her."
msgstr ""

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:1768
msgid "Wow, you guys are good."
msgstr ""

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:1773
msgid " *wink* *wink*"
msgstr ""

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:1779
msgid "Here, this will help her."
msgstr ""

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:1790
#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:1879
msgid "Uh....... where..... am..... I...?"
msgstr ""

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:1795
msgid ""
"You are in the dungeons of Malifor. These brave people have just released "
"you."
msgstr ""

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:1802
#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:1890
msgid "....thanks."
msgstr "...grazie."

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:1808
msgid ""
"No problem. Sister Theta, you take care of her. If she wants to join us she "
"would make a powerful ally."
msgstr ""

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:1814
#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:1902
msgid "Yes, I would... like to join... you Lord Tallin."
msgstr ""

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:1820
msgid ""
"Just Tallin; I am no lord. But gee, that sure is some powerful spell you "
"used on her, Sister. She is looking better already."
msgstr ""

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:1827
msgid "And I feel better too. Now let's get back at that disgusting skeleton."
msgstr ""

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:1833
#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:1925
msgid "Why did the bag of bones capture you in the first place?"
msgstr ""

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:1839
#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:1931
msgid "Because he thought I was pretty."
msgstr ""

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:1845
#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:1937
msgid "That old skeleton? Geez, what a nutcase."
msgstr ""

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:1851
#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:1943
msgid "You're telling me."
msgstr ""

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:1868
msgid ""
"I wish we had some healers with us. Just try to help her the best you can."
msgstr ""

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:1873
msgid "Here, I hope that helps."
msgstr ""

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:1884
msgid "You are in the dungeons of Malifor. We have just released you."
msgstr ""

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:1896
msgid ""
"No problem. Just take it easy. If you would like to join us your help could "
"mean life or death for a lot of us."
msgstr ""

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:1908
#, fuzzy
msgid "Just Tallin, I am no lord. And you are looking better already."
msgstr "Solo Tallin, niente lord. E non c'è di che."

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:1919
msgid ""
"Oh, just a few tricks I know, otherwise I probably would be dead by now. But "
"let's get back at that disgusting skeleton."
msgstr ""

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:1973
msgid "Holy cow! What did I just let out of that cage! Look out everyone."
msgstr ""

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:1979
msgid "Oooooh, cool, it's a drake!"
msgstr ""

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:1984
msgid " *whimper*"
msgstr ""

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:1989
msgid ""
"My God, such a fierce creature whimpering! What the heck have they done to "
"it?"
msgstr ""

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:1995
msgid "The bastards!"
msgstr "Che bastardi!"

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:2000
msgid "Probably another one of Malifor's experiments."
msgstr "Probabilmente è un'altro degli esperimenti di Malifor."

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:2007
msgid "I don't know, see if it talks."
msgstr "Non so, vediamo se parla."

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:2012
msgid "Hey, big guy. We aren't gonna hurt you. We wanna be your friends."
msgstr "Ehi, ragazzone. Non ti faremo del male. Vogliamo diventare tuoi amici."

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:2017
msgid ".....not..... going..... to...... hurt.... me?"
msgstr "... non... mi... farete... del... male?"

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:2023
msgid "Hey, it talks!"
msgstr "Ehi, parla!"

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:2029
msgid "It's a 'he', and  yes, they're actually very intelligent creatures."
msgstr "Eh sì, in realtà sono creature molto intelligenti."

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:2034
msgid ""
"Hush! I am trying to talk to him. Nope, we'll never hurt you. But if you "
"want to you can hurt some skeletons."
msgstr ""
"Zitto! Sto cercando di parlare con lui. No, non ti faremo del male. Ma se "
"vuoi, possiamo distruggere qualche scheletro assieme."

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:2039
msgid "Skeletons! GRRRRRRRR!!!"
msgstr "Scheletri! GRRRRRRRR!!!"

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:2044
msgid "Look out! He is ready to go! Hey, is that smoke coming out of his ears?"
msgstr ""
"Gaurdate! È proprio pronto per andare! Ehi, cos'è quel fumo che gli esce "
"dalle orecchie?"

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:2049
msgid ""
"Hey, there is an escape tunnel right behind this cell. The hole wasn't big "
"enough for me to go through but one of you might fit."
msgstr ""

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:2054
msgid "I see it. Hmmm, it is pretty small, let's see if we can make it bigger."
msgstr ""

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:2065
msgid "There we go. Now let's see where this tunnel leads to."
msgstr ""

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:2077
msgid "ROOOOOOAAAARRRR!"
msgstr "ROOOOOOAAAARRRR!"

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:2082
msgid ""
"Woha! Maybe he isn't so friendly after all... or at least to some things."
msgstr ""

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:2100
msgid "HAHAHAHAHA, FOOLS, YOU THINK YOU CAN KILL ME?"
msgstr "AHAHAHAHAH, SCIOCCHI, PENSATE DI POTERMI UCCIDERE?"

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:2153
msgid "What the...!"
msgstr "Ma che... !"

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:2158
msgid "How can it be?! Our axes and hammers are failing."
msgstr ""

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:2164
msgid "Blast it! Now where did he go? Let's find him and try something else!"
msgstr ""

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:2169
#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:2289
#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:2409
#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:2525
msgid "I see now. It is impossible to destroy him by ordinary means."
msgstr ""

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:2176
#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:2296
#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:2416
#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:2532
msgid "Then how are we going to destroy him? Surely there must be a way."
msgstr ""

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:2181
#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:2301
#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:2421
msgid ""
"Yes, I think there is, but only myself or Theta have the means to do it. "
"Come on Theta, let's destroy that old skeleton."
msgstr ""

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:2187
#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:2307
#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:2427
#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:2543
msgid "Yeah, I can't wait to get my hands on that bastard!"
msgstr ""

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:2193
#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:2313
#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:2433
#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:2549
msgid "That was very unladylike of you."
msgstr ""

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:2199
#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:2319
#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:2439
#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:2555
msgid " *giggle* Sorry."
msgstr ""

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:2220
msgid "HAHAHAHAHAHA, YOUR IDIOCY AMUSES ME GREATLY!"
msgstr "AHAHAHAHAHAH, LA TUA STUPIDITÀ È DAVVERO DIVERTENTE!"

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:2243
msgid "COME AND GET ME!"
msgstr "VENITE A PRENDERMI!"

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:2249
msgid "Geez, how are we going to kill him?"
msgstr ""

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:2254
msgid "Well, obviously clubs and arrows won't work."
msgstr "Be', naturalmente mazze e frecce non servono."

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:2260
msgid "Oh darn, he disappeared. Let's find him and try a different weapon."
msgstr "Oh dannato, è scomparso. Troviamolo e proviamo un'altra arma."

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:2340
msgid "HAHAHAHAHAHA, DEATH HAS NO EFFECT ON ME YOU FOOLS!"
msgstr "AHAHAHAHAHAH, LA MORTE NON HA EFFETTO SU DI ME, SCIOCCHI!"

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:2363
msgid "HAHAHAHAHA, I CAN NEVER BE DESTROYED!"
msgstr "AHAHAHAHAHA, NON POTRÒ MAI ESSERE DISTRUTTO!"

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:2369
msgid "No, there has to be a way!"
msgstr "No, ci deve essere un modo!"

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:2374
msgid "Well, it isn't gonna be blades."
msgstr "Be', non saranno le spade."

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:2380
msgid "And look, he's gone. Now we gotta find him all over again!"
msgstr "E guarda, se ne è andato. Adesso dobbiamo di nuovo cercarlo da capo!"

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:2461
msgid "HAHAHAHAHAHA, I AM IMMORTAL!"
msgstr "AHAHAHAHAHAH, SONO IMMORTALE!"

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:2508
msgid "YOU PUNY MORTALS SHALL SOON BE SERVING ME!"
msgstr "YOU PUNY MORTALS PRESTO SARETE AL MIO SERVIZIO!"

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:2514
msgid "That blasted skeleton! Even fire has no affect on him!"
msgstr "Dannato scheletro! Nemmeno il fuoco ha effetto su di lui!"

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:2520
msgid ""
"Look, he disappeared again. Let's find him and try using a different weapon "
"on him."
msgstr ""
"Guarda, è di nuovo scomparso. Troviamolo e proviamo un'altra arma su di lui."

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:2537
msgid ""
"Yes, I think there is, but only myself or Theta have the means to do it. "
"Come on, Theta, let's destroy that old skeleton."
msgstr ""

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:2575
msgid "AHHHHHH! YOU BLASTED MAGE!"
msgstr "AHHHHHH! MAGO MALEDETTO!"

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:2581
msgid "Good. We finally got him. He is just dissolving."
msgstr "Bene. Lo abbiamo preso. Si sta già dissolvendo."

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:2587
msgid ""
"Curses on you you blasted mages, curses on you you blasted dwarves, curses "
"on you you blasted humans, and CURSES ON YOU YOU BLASTED TALLIN! MAY YOUR "
"MISERABLE LIVES BE FULL OF TORTURE! MAY YOUR PEOPLE NEVER BE FREE! MAY ALL "
"YOUR NEAR AND DEAR DESERT YOU! MAY A THUNDERBOLT HIT YOUR HEAD! MAY..."
msgstr ""

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:2610
msgid "At last! Victory is ours! Good work, men!."
msgstr "Finalmente! Abbiamo vinto! Ben lavoro, uomini!"

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:2615
msgid "So where to now, Tallin?"
msgstr "Dove andiamo adesso, Tallin?"

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:2622
msgid ""
"Now, let's get back to the dwarves and see what progress they have made in "
"forging us weapons."
msgstr ""

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:2643
msgid "They are trying to free the prisoners! Stop them!"
msgstr ""

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:2648
msgid "Good luck, my friend."
msgstr "Buona fortuna, amico mio."

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:2699
#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:3117
msgid "Intruders! Get them!"
msgstr "Intrusi! Prendeteli!"

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:2704
#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:3122
msgid "Bring it on!"
msgstr ""

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:2778
msgid ""
"They are attacking the master's study! We must stop them! Call the reserves!"
msgstr ""

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:2783
msgid " 'The master's study' eh? I bet we'll find Mailfor there!"
msgstr ""

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:2847
msgid "Ugh, a dead body!"
msgstr "Agh, un morto!"

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:2863
msgid "Here's another body."
msgstr "Qui ce n'è un altro."

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:2879
msgid "And another..."
msgstr "E un altro ancora..."

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:2895
msgid ""
"Gee, what's with all these bodies floating around? Is this river some sort "
"of body disposal?"
msgstr ""

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:2911
msgid "The Great Chamber"
msgstr ""

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:2916
msgid " 'The Great Chamber'? Hmmm, wonder what that could be."
msgstr ""

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:2932
msgid ""
"So This is the Great Chamber eh? Doesen't look like there is much to see "
"here."
msgstr ""
"Quindi questa è la grande camera, eh? Non mi pare ci sia molto da vedere qua."

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:2939
msgid " *rumble*"
msgstr ""

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:2944
msgid "Uh oh, I think I spoke too soon."
msgstr "Oh oh, mi sa che ho parlato troppo presto."

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:2953
#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:3057
#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:3332
#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:3516
msgid " *CRASH*"
msgstr ""

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:2960
msgid ""
"What was that? Oh shoot - there are two big slabs of rock cutting off our "
"retreat!"
msgstr ""

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:3068
msgid "Hsssssssss"
msgstr "Hsssssssss"

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:3073
msgid "This doesn't look good."
msgstr ""

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:3079
msgid "Great Chamber my foot! It should be called, 'The Death Chamber.'"
msgstr ""

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:3099
msgid "Here we go."
msgstr "Eccoci."

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:3228
msgid "Halt! Who goes there? Friend or foe?"
msgstr "Alt! Chi va là? Amico o nemico?"

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:3233
msgid "Depends. Are you loyal to Malifor?"
msgstr "Dipende. Sei leale a Malifor?"

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:3238
msgid ""
"Never! If you ha' been sent by Malifor, then know that we will never yield! "
"Come and meet your death!"
msgstr ""
"Giammai! Se siete stati mandati da Malifor, sappiate che non cederemo mai. "
"Venite avanti per incontrare la vostra morte!"

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:3243
msgid ""
"Hold!  We aren't friends of Malifor in the least. Rather, we have come to "
"destroy him."
msgstr ""
"Un momento! Non siamo affatto amici di Malinor. Piuttosto, veniamo per "
"distruggerlo."

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:3248
msgid "Finally! You don't know how long we have been waiting for this day."
msgstr "Finalmente! Non sapete quanto abbiamo aspettato questo giorno."

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:3253
msgid "How did you get here and how long have you been here?"
msgstr "Come siete arrivati qui e da quanto tempo siete qui?"

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:3258
msgid ""
"We were originally prisoners of Malifor, but we tunnelled out and escaped. "
"Since then, we have eked out a precarious survival on what we have been able "
"to steal or raid from Malifor."
msgstr ""

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:3263
msgid "By now you have tunnels all through this place."
msgstr ""

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:3268
msgid ""
"Aye. That seemingly blank wall to the south there is actually a hidden "
"entrance to the treasury."
msgstr ""

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:3273
msgid "Awesome, let's go!"
msgstr ""

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:3289
msgid ""
" *sigh* Great. More water. And there doesn't seem to be anything down this "
"tunnel, either friend or foe."
msgstr ""

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:3313
msgid "Hmmm, another door. Boy, is this one sure locked up."
msgstr "Mh, un'altra porta. Ragazzi, questa è chiusa a chiave per bene."

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:3319
msgid "Anything you can't handle?"
msgstr "È un compito troppo difficile per te?"

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:3324
msgid "Nope. Should I open it?"
msgstr "Per niente. Devo aprirla?"

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:3328
#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:3694
msgid "Go for it!"
msgstr "Certo, fallo!"

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:3346
#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:3530
#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:3757
msgid "There we go."
msgstr "Andiamo."

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:3375
#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:3552
#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:3780
msgid "You wretched vermin, I have had it with you! Guards!"
msgstr "Maledetti parassiti, ne ho abbastanza di voi! Guardie!"

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:3475
#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:3642
#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:3883
msgid "Just wait a sec."
msgstr "Aspetta un attimo."

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:3509
msgid ""
"It looks like this is it. Here is the door to Malifor's study. Are we all "
"ready for this?"
msgstr ""

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:3512
msgid "Yeah, open those doors!"
msgstr "Sì, apri quella porta!"

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:3679
msgid "Hey, check this out, it looks like some sort of lever."
msgstr "Ehi, guardate qui, sembra una specie di leva."

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:3685
msgid "Probably for that door right there."
msgstr "Probabilmente è per quella porta lì."

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:3690
msgid "Should I throw it?"
msgstr "Devo tirarla?"

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:3699
msgid "Ok, here we go!"
msgstr "Bene, eccoci qui."

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:3704
msgid " *creak*....."
msgstr ""

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:3709
msgid "Nothing. That door is not moving."
msgstr "Niente. La porta non si sposta."

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:3714
msgid "Why don't you try 'knocking'."
msgstr "Perché non provi a \"bussare\"?"

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:3719
msgid "Ok."
msgstr "Va bene."

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:3724
#, fuzzy
msgid " *BANG*"
msgstr " *BANG*"

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:3729
msgid "Anybody home?"
msgstr "C'è nessuno in casa?"

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:3734
msgid " *BOOM*"
msgstr ""

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/The_Pursuit.cfg:3739
#, fuzzy
msgid " *CRASH!!!*"
msgstr " *CRASH!!!*"

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/To_The_Mines.cfg:6
msgid "To the Mines"
msgstr "Alle miniere"

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/To_The_Mines.cfg:10
msgid ""
"After reaching the dwarvish keep and tending to their wounded the humans led "
"by Tallin and the dwarves led by Lord Hamel made council."
msgstr ""
"Dopo essere giunti alla fortezza dei nani e aver curato i feriti, gli uomini "
"sotto il comando di Tallin, e i nani condotti da lord Hamel si riunirono in "
"consiglio."

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/To_The_Mines.cfg:14
msgid ""
"Be welcome to the Southern Tunnels friends... or at least, what's left o' "
"them."
msgstr ""
"Benvenuti alle gallerie meridionali, amici... o almeno, a ciò che ne resta."

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/To_The_Mines.cfg:19
msgid ""
"Thank you, Lord Hamel. Though Knalga lies in chaos, it is a great relief to "
"see that at least some dwarves have survived."
msgstr ""
"Grazie, lord Hamel. Anche se Knalga è nel caos, è un gran sollievo vedere "
"che almeno alcuni nani sono riusciti a sopravvivere."

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/To_The_Mines.cfg:24
msgid ""
"Thank you, human. It is likewise a great relief to see that our allies of "
"old have managed to break their bonds, and live as free men once again."
msgstr ""
"Grazie, uomo. È anche un gran sollievo vedere che i nostri antichi alleati "
"sono riusciti a spezzare le catene e a vivere di nuovo da uomini liberi."

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/To_The_Mines.cfg:29
msgid ""
"Yes, that touches on the main reason for our visit. We have broken free, but "
"to stay free we need better weapons and armor.  Clubs and pitchforks wll not "
"carry us through the long run."
msgstr ""
"Sì, questo è il motivo principale della nostra visita. Siamo riusciti a "
"liberarci, ma per restare liberi, ci servono armi e armature migliori. "
"Randelli e forconi non saranno sufficienti, a lungo andare."

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/To_The_Mines.cfg:34
msgid ""
"Dwarves are known to be the finest metalworkers and weapon-smiths. We were "
"hoping that you would be able to help us."
msgstr ""
"I nani sono noti come i migliori metallurghi e armaioli. Noi speriamo che "
"possiate aiutarci."

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/To_The_Mines.cfg:39
msgid ""
"Aye, our craft is great...but we dinna ha' much of weapons and armor "
"ourselves. We're but a remnant that survived the orcs' in-taking of these "
"caves.  There may be other remnants; but if there are, we dinna yet ken of "
"them."
msgstr ""

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/To_The_Mines.cfg:44
msgid ""
"Some months gone we had the luck to kill the warlord who controlled the "
"caves.  The orcs began squabbling among themselves over who would succeed "
"him at the very moment they night ha' crushed us, else I and mine wouldna' "
"be here to greet you."
msgstr ""

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/To_The_Mines.cfg:49
msgid ""
"We ha' been stranded in these tunnels for years now, almost completely cut "
"off from sources of food or metals or tools.  It has been as much as we "
"could do to survive.  We'll ha' more food again now that we can reach the "
"surface, and tools aplenty there are in the stores where we couldna' reach "
"while the orcs held them.  But metal will be scarce for a while yet; ore "
"will have to be briught in for smelting, first."
msgstr ""

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/To_The_Mines.cfg:54
msgid "Is there any source of good ores nearby?"
msgstr ""

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/To_The_Mines.cfg:59
msgid ""
"Aye, there is. A few miles north of here is the place where we mined many of "
"our raw metals. However, that place also seems to be where all those "
"skeletons are coming from. To go there would mean certain death."
msgstr ""

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/To_The_Mines.cfg:64
msgid ""
"What is the story with those skeletons anyway? They look like they were "
"dwarves at one point but now they just attack everyone and anyone."
msgstr ""

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/To_The_Mines.cfg:69
msgid ""
"In truth, we ha' no idea. They just started appearing one day some years "
"after we were trapped here."
msgstr ""
"Per essere franco, non ne ho idea. Sono comparsi improvvisamente qualche "
"anno dopo il momento in cui siamo stati intrappolati qui."

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/To_The_Mines.cfg:74
msgid ""
"Perhaps if we go there we can find out. Let us combine our forces and march "
"to the mines and settle this mater once and for all."
msgstr ""

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/To_The_Mines.cfg:79
msgid ""
"That way we can gather what we need to begin turning the tide against those "
"orcs... I know it will be extremely dangerous, but it is better to die "
"trying then to sit idle and slowly starve to death."
msgstr ""

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/To_The_Mines.cfg:84
msgid ""
"Aye, ye've the right of it, lad. Form, up men! To the mines! Let the "
"guardsmen stay behind along with the noncombatants - for their safety and to "
"hold the keep."
msgstr ""

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/To_The_Mines.cfg:89
msgid ""
"There are two ways we can go from here. One is through the tunnels and the "
"other is to leave the tunnels and go through the mountains. Both ways are "
"about the same length. If you go though the tunnels we'll be facing more "
"trolls and perhaps skeletons. If we take the mountains - who knows. So what "
"will it be?"
msgstr ""

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/To_The_Mines.cfg:94
msgid ""
"I don't think I'm all that crazy about facing those trolls again any time "
"soon. Let's take the mountain route."
msgstr ""
"Non penso di essere così folle da affrontare di nuovo questi troll tanto "
"presto. Prendiamo la strada delle montagne."

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/To_The_Mines.cfg:189
msgid "Once the party left the caves they found that they faced a new threat."
msgstr ""
"Quando il gruppo uscì dalle caverne, si trovò ad affrontare una nuova "
"minaccia."

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/To_The_Mines.cfg:194
msgid "Hey look, there is our meat! Come on, boys, lunchtime!"
msgstr "Ehi, guarda, ecco la nostra carne! Venite ragazzi, è ora di pranzo!"

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/To_The_Mines.cfg:200
msgid "I don't think so, buddy."
msgstr "Non credo proprio, amico."

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/To_The_Mines.cfg:233
msgid "Argh! They are stronger then we thought. Someone go tell the Master..."
msgstr ""
"Argh! Sono più forti del previsto. Qualcuno vada a riferirlo al padrone..."

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/To_The_Mines.cfg:239
msgid "What's with this 'Master' business? It's starting to make me nervous."
msgstr ""
"Che cos'è tutto questo parlare di «padrone»? Comincia a rendermi nervoso."

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/To_The_Mines.cfg:255
msgid "OK, here is the entrance to the dwarven mines.  In we go!"
msgstr "Bene, ecco l'ingresso alle miniere dei nani, andiamo!"

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/To_The_Mines.cfg:260
msgid ""
"Hey, there goes our lunch! Hmmm, they are stronger then we thought, let's go "
"tell Master."
msgstr ""
"Ehi, il nostro pranzo se ne va! Hmmm, sono più forti di quanto credevamo, "
"andiamo a dirlo al padrone."

#: Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/To_The_Mines.cfg:266
msgid ""
"What's with this whole 'Master' business? It's starting to make me nervous."
msgstr ""
"Che cos'è tutto questo parlare di «padrone»? Comincia a rendermi nervoso."

